"content": "<h2>Engraving on the high priest's equipment</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:9-Exod28:12\">EXO 28:9–28:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:21\">EXO 28:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:36\">EXO 28:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:6\">EXO 39:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:14\">EXO 39:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:30\">EXO 39:30</a></p>\n<h2>Engraving in the temple</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr2:7\">2CH 2:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:31\">1KI 7:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:36\">1KI 7:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr2:14\">2CH 2:14</a></p>\n<h2>Engraving on stone</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job19:24\">JOB 19:24</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech3:9\">ZEC 3:9</a></p>\n<h2>The Ten Commandments engraved on tablets</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod32:15-Exod32:16\">EXO 32:15–32:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor3:7-2Cor3:8\">2CO 3:7–3:8</a></p>\n<h2>Figurative use of engraving</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:16\">ISA 49:16</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer17:1\">JER 17:1</a></strong></p>",
